501
00:40:35,599 --> 00:40:38,102
I hope you'll understand, Mr. Seon-jun.

502
00:40:38,185 --> 00:40:39,937
Oh please. There's nothing to discuss.

503
00:40:40,521 --> 00:40:42,565
With friendships between
people of our caliber,

504
00:40:42,648 --> 00:40:44,358
